  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Cook the sausages in a pan over medium heat until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "In a separate pan, cook the garlic and onion until softened, about 3 minutes.",
    "Add the mashed potatoes to the pan and stir to combine with garlic and onion.",
    "Transfer the sausage mixture to a baking dish and top with mashed potato mixture.",
    "Sprinkle bread crumbs on top and drizzle with malt vinegar.",
    "Bake in the preheated oven for 20 minutes, or until the top is golden brown.",
    "Garnish with bonito flakes and serve hot.",
    "Serve with your favorite sides, such as toast or a salad."
